l oil supply-demand balance, the prospects for the trading of oil products, and the development of the oil refining industry in the region.Global Oil Trends is valuable not only for those in the oil industry but also for academicians, energy planners, university students who are concerned with the global oil situation and the dynamism of the Asia-Pacific oil market.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Industries / Energy.2bisacsh1 aDabbaransi, H.E. Korn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDatuk, H.E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDaud, Sulaiman Hj., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKennedy, John L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aL.H. Tan, Joseph, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMarashian, Onnic, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSandhu, K.S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSharma, Shankar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSharma, Shankar, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTakahashi, Kiyoshi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTan, Joseph L.H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVerleger, Philip K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Archive (pre 2000) eBook Packagez978311064968008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertISEAS Archive eBook-Package 1970-1999z978311060669040uhttps://doi.org/10.1355/978981437939740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789814379397423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789814379397.jpg  a